b'      Allare invited to attend  Friday\'s (April 8)  talk in our "Leadership Lecture Series" by Shri. Mayank Kachhwaha ( BTME, \'08 ), Cofounder IndiaLends,   IC & SR Auditorium at 5 pm   Title:  Entrepreneurship: The first 12 months   Abstract : Mayank Kachhwaha shares his own experience of the competencies, resources, and team one needs to survive and do well in the first year.   Biography :  Forbes India \'30 Under 30\' Entrepreneur, Mayank Kachhwaha has over seven years of global experience in the credit risk and lending industry. He cofounded IndiaLends  India\'s fastest growing credit underwriting and risk analytics platform that connects consumers with financial institutions to get the best credit products  in 2015. Prior to this, he worked in risk assessment and consumer analytics, financial modelling, and financial operations design roles in the US, UK, and Indian Markets. He graduated in the year 2008 with a B Tech in Mechanical Engineering.  Besides being an Entrepreneur, he loves playing the guitar, watching football and cooking.  With regards....  Prof. R. Nagarajan  Department of Chemical Engineering Dean, International & Alumni Relations IIT Madras  email: deaniar@iitm.ac.in Phone: +91 9444008390 _____________________________________  '

